asset.hookText:
Subscribe to our channel:
http://bit.ly/12dY9oO

Do you constantly find your Chihuahua running sprints up and down the stairs? Has your Chihuahua attempted to run the straightaway against a cheetah? Does your Chihuahua run so fast in circles, it often looks like a swirling blur? If you think your Chihuahua has what it takes, PETCO is calling out to all Chihuahuas to enter in their Chihuahua Race!

Something extraordinary happens when pets and people connect. A unique bond is formed that results in something powerful, not only between pets and people, but in a way that makes the world a better place. Our promise is to nurture that relationship completely--mind and body.
